{"tid":492821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：討論港獨結論必須是港獨不切實際","createTime":"2017-12-08T02:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T04:49:29.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"38497f8613126eb2aa985903f7e27c3eab66365c","tid":492821,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:10:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">楊潤雄：討論港獨結論必須是港獨不切實際</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】教育局局長楊潤雄被問到近期有學生派發港獨單張是否觸犯煽動罪，他指由執法機關處理，重申教師與學生討論港獨時結論必須是港獨不切實際。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=245846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D245846&d=WhVtFhm6MzdxFGSq8%2FK8QcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=3c135306\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D245846&h=44eab829\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=245846</a>"},{"pid":"ed5b9d5870a30f6136ccf8e57e9047e5c76e7fec","tid":492821,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"駐連登獨派代表HKVDC_2017水已潛"},{"pid":"037004cb3b172d6b629c7ab132a62fcccee7c584","tid":492821,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:22:04.000Z","msg":"共狗是咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野同上年考評局歴史問你是當時知識份子是否支持支那共產黨 相信佢地民主一樣<br />\n<br />\n如果你知共產黨個唯物史觀 講左共產必是所有社會最後型態<br />\n<br />\n如果係民主下 投出非共產社會會點<br />\n就無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b88e258525204397dc848f713a5c7f8c470cf08","tid":492821,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:23:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共狗是咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野同上年考評局歴史問你是當時知識份子是否支持支那共產黨 相信佢地民主一樣<br />\n<br />\n如果你知共產黨個唯物史觀 講左共產必是所有社會最後型態<br />\n<br />\n如果係民主下 投出非共產社會會點<br />\n就無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共